Author: xxobutitoldyouso
Text: I tried to get quest bars but they are way to expensive for me.   Since i've never had one then i like to pretend they are not worth the hype.  Broke on December </3 that sucks   Being broke on January and crying over low cal food ftw (???)

Author: colderbytheminute
Text: God knows how much money I've spent on damn Quest bars and diet soda. And dumb keto/low carb baked goods that I binge on anyway. I was broke the entire December just from food.
